## Learning, Performance, and Observability

- **Effectiveness Assessment**: [pkg/ai/insights/assessor.go](pkg/ai/insights/assessor.go) -- Track outcomes, adjust confidence scores
- **Pattern Discovery**: [pkg/intelligence/patterns/pattern_discovery_engine.go](pkg/intelligence/patterns/pattern_discovery_engine.go) -- Recurring alert patterns, action-outcome correlation
- **Caching**: Cache embedding results with TTL; store frequent AI responses in Redis
- **Batch Processing**: Group similar alerts for batch analysis; balance latency vs. throughput
- **Monitoring**: Track response times, success rates, confidence distributions, and costs per provider
- **Cost Management**: Implement budget alerts/quotas; optimize prompt size; use appropriate model tiers

